attributes.title: I died. I actually died
attributes.review: I was very ecstatic to download this app so I could be in lightened of all of the wonderful thing our orange says. It started off with me trying to download it. And that’s when the problem started. It took 27 years to download. I was willing to do it for our president though. After 27 years it finally downloaded and I was very excited. But as soon as I went on it was so glitchy and nothing was working. I still try to keep using it despite all of the problems. After a while of using this app I started to get weird sensation in my stomach all the time. It hurts so bad. It started off small but then it got worse and worse and worse. It hurts so much I went to the doctors. They said an orange tree was growing inside of me.He also told me that it is not removable and they can try their best to try to get it out but it is very rare to survive this. They tried everything they could but the orange tree would not come out. Every day I was in so much pain. The pain was unbearable. And then one day I died. Yes you heard me right I died.I am now a ghost writing this and warning all of you not to download this app or there will be an orange tree growing inside of you and you will die. Please just give this app a one star rating to respect my death. I was a young and beautiful person and I wish I had lived my life longer. But you guys can save yourselves from this baboon called our president. Thank you for listening to my TedTalk.
